<div style="text-align:center">
    Thank you for visiting the Aurora Bricks Store. Protecting your private information is our priority. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website [insert website URL], including any other media form, media channel, mobile website, or mobile application related or connected thereto (collectively, the "Site").

