    Security of your Information
</div>

We use industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, misuse, or alteration. However, no method of transmission over the Internet, or method of electronic storage, is 100% secure. Therefore, while we strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your personal information, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.

<br />
<br />
